Color Picker Tool Documentation:-

Overview
This Color Picker Tool is a simple web-based application that allows users to select a color using various methods and apply it to change the background color of the screen. It provides options to choose colors through a color picker input and offers fine control using sliders for Hue, Saturation, and Value (HSV).

Files Included:-
index.html: Contains the HTML structure of the color picker tool.
styles.css: Defines the styles for the HTML elements to create the visual appearance.
script.js: Contains JavaScript code responsible for the functionality of the color picker tool.

HTML Structure (index.html)
Color Box: <div class="color-box" id="color-box"></div> - Represents the area displaying the selected color.
Color Picker Input: <input type="color" id="color-picker" value="#ffffff"> - Allows direct color selection using a color picker.

HSV Controls:
Hue: <input type="range" id="hue" min="0" max="360" value="0">
Saturation: <input type="range" id="saturation" min="0" max="100" value="100">
Value: <input type="range" id="value" min="0" max="100" value="100">
These sliders offer control over the Hue, Saturation, and Value components of the selected color.

CSS Styles (styles.css)
Defines the visual appearance of the color picker tool, including layout, colors, and sizing of elements.

JavaScript Functionality (script.js)
updateColor(): Updates the selected color based on the current values of Hue, Saturation, and Value.
Event Listeners:
colorPicker: Listens to changes in the color picker input and updates the color box accordingly.
hueInput, saturationInput, valueInput: Listens to changes in HSV sliders and triggers the update of the selected color.
Initialization: Initializes the color picker tool by setting default values and colors.


Usage
Open the index.html file in a web browser.
Use the color picker input to directly choose a color.
Adjust the HSV sliders to fine-tune the selected color.
The background color of the screen will change dynamically based on the selected color.


Customization
Adjust the styles in styles.css to modify the appearance of the color picker tool.
Modify JavaScript functions in script.js to add additional functionalities or customize behaviors.
